ecies$\backslash$ncomposition, with the presence of three tree species playing a$\backslash$nsignificant role. Microclimate explained 31.4{\%} of the variance in$\backslash$ndecomposition, and was related to lower soil moisture. Within this$\backslash$nmicroclimate effect, species diversity (without composition) explained$\backslash$n8.9{\%} and topography 34.4{\%} of variance. Topography mainly affected$\backslash$ndiurnal temperature amplitudes by varying incident solar radiation.},
